{
  "texts": [
    "We used the target models for generation and labeling within May-June, 2023, meaning model endpoints available during this time was used.",
    "So a reproduction should be aimed at using versions of the models during this time (if in case model has been updated).",
    "The prompting configuration for both models is same and presented in Table 7.",
    "We use the same configuration for a generation as well as labeling.",
    "While the full data of 157k generations are provided in supplementary material, some examples across various pivots are presented in Figure 10."
  ]
}